first sentence of the video,

00:34:22.092 --> 00:34:23.550
it's a great
technique to make sure

00:34:23.550 --> 00:34:27.151
that your audience is caught
up with you all the time.

00:34:27.151 --> 00:34:28.900
And I say everywhere
except the first bit,

00:34:28.900 --> 00:34:31.840
because the exception
is that if you

00:34:31.840 --> 00:34:34.070
want to start with
a compelling hook,

00:34:34.070 --> 00:34:36.000
you might start
completely out of order,

00:34:36.000 --> 00:34:38.250
and then come back to
something later in the video

00:34:38.250 --> 00:34:40.166
just for the purposes
of hooking your audience

00:34:40.166 --> 00:34:43.370
and getting them through
the first 10 seconds.

00:34:43.370 --> 00:34:46.409
But other than that,
that sort of expansion--

00:34:46.409 --> 00:34:48.239
I sort of look at
it as a funnel.

00:34:48.239 --> 00:34:51.449
You start really simple,
and then work your way out

00:34:51.449 --> 00:34:53.296
to complicated.

00:34:53.296 --> 00:34:54.232
What else?

00:34:56.898 --> 00:34:58.606
AUDIENCE: I'm not
