00:41:09.020 --> 00:41:11.940
GEORGE ZAIDAN: And following
that even further--

00:41:11.940 --> 00:41:14.550
I just had a
question in my mind.

00:41:14.550 --> 00:41:17.640
Let's say you took two people.

00:41:17.640 --> 00:41:19.610
One who can wear shorts
