01:23:10.260 --> 01:23:12.848
build with a shoebox,
and then just see

01:23:12.848 --> 01:23:14.394
how it progressively floats.

01:23:14.394 --> 01:23:16.310
GEORGE ZAIDAN: So the
problem with the Titanic

01:23:16.310 --> 01:23:18.320
was that their
compartments did not extend

01:23:18.320 --> 01:23:19.660
