01:23:19.660 --> 01:23:21.629
AUDIENCE: All the way
up the [INAUDIBLE].

01:23:21.629 --> 01:23:22.420
GEORGE ZAIDAN: Why?

01:23:22.420 --> 01:23:23.086
That seems dumb.

01:23:23.086 --> 01:23:24.600
AUDIENCE: I have no idea.

01:23:24.600 --> 01:23:26.100
AUDIENCE: But then
the video becomes

01:23:26.100 --> 01:23:28.930
