01:27:23.530 --> 01:27:25.600
a lot of potential for it.

01:27:25.600 --> 01:27:28.970
So just a word of encouragement.

01:27:28.970 --> 01:27:30.470
GEORGE ZAIDAN: Yeah,
I would totally

01:27:30.470 --> 01:27:32.855
