01:28:29.970 --> 01:28:32.600
So why even get braces
in the first place?

01:28:32.600 --> 01:28:35.314
Cut to pictures of famous
stars who have had braces

01:28:35.314 --> 01:28:36.022
with a voiceover.

01:28:39.980 --> 01:28:40.689
Should I keep--

01:28:40.689 --> 01:28:42.480
GEORGE ZAIDAN: Yep,
just the next sentence.

01:28:42.480 --> 01:28:43.150
GUEST SPEAKER:
Studies have shown

01:28:43.150 --> 01:28:45.480
that having a beautiful
smile with even white teeth

01:28:45.480 --> 01:28:48.950
conveys health and youth, and
makes people like you even

01:28:48.950 --> 01:28:50.280
a little bit more.

01:28:50.280 --> 01:28:51.590
GEORGE ZAIDAN: Cool, thanks.

01:28:51.590 --> 01:28:55.530
Who were the famous stars
that you are thinking of here?

01:28:55.530 --> 01:28:56.930
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

01:29:20.380 --> 01:29:23.324
AUDIENCE: But this
video's about you.

01:29:23.324 --> 01:29:24.990
AUDIENCE: Well the
way that I structured

01:29:24.990 --> 01:29:27.830
it is to have as
little of me in it

01:29:27.830 --> 01:29:31.770
as possible, which is why I
had so much of the [INAUDIBLE].

01:29:31.770 --> 01:29:33.690
There would only be
one or two choices.

01:29:33.690 --> 01:29:35.870
GEORGE ZAIDAN: Just
out of curiosity, why?

01:29:35.870 --> 01:29:39.127
Why did you structure
it that way?

01:29:39.127 --> 01:29:40.710
AUDIENCE: I like the
animation aspect.

01:29:40.710 --> 01:29:44.410
I also know I don't
look good on camera.

01:29:47.450 --> 01:29:52.190
AUDIENCE: No one knows that
they don't look at my camera.

01:29:52.190 --> 01:29:53.870
AUDIENCE: I feel
like this is the fear

01:29:53.870 --> 01:29:57.097
that every person comes into
