01:34:22.190 --> 01:34:26.510
get into the hosting side?

01:34:26.510 --> 01:34:28.752
AUDIENCE: I like the
first paragraph especially

01:34:28.752 --> 01:34:30.460
GEORGE ZAIDAN: What
