02:01:29.590 --> 02:01:30.400
unfamiliar.

02:01:30.400 --> 02:01:35.340
So you can even get away from
the idea of getting braces.

02:01:35.340 --> 02:01:36.870
This is something
we do, but rather

02:01:36.870 --> 02:01:42.590
start with this monstrous
thing that we dissolve our jaw.

02:01:42.590 --> 02:01:44.390
And that's a really cool image.

02:01:44.390 --> 02:01:46.090
And maybe you put
